<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>KidFit | Kindergarten Learning Reimagined</title>

    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quicksand:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Setup favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="~/static/favicon-96x96.png" sizes="96x96" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="~/static/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="~/static/favicon.ico" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/home.css">
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="./static/logo.png" alt="KidFit logo" class="logo-placeholder">
            KidFit
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <span class="section-tag">New for 2025</span> <!-- Dynamic year change in JS -->
        <h1>Play. Learn. Grow. Together.</h1>
        <p>Combining the tactile joy of physical flashcards with a powerful digital hub designed specifically for kindergarten teachers.</p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
            <a href="#product" class="cta-button" style="background: var(--secondary);">Explore Product</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="importance" id="about">
        <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">Bridge the gap between Screen and Play</h2>
        <div class="importance-grid">
            <div class="card fade-in">
                <h3>Sensory Learning</h3>
                <p>Research shows kids under 6 learn best through physical touch and high-contrast illustrations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card fade-in">
                <h3>Teacher-First</h3>
                <p>Designed to reduce prep time by 40%, letting educators focus on what matters: the children.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card fade-in">
                <h3>Modern Curriculum</h3>
                <p>Content updated seasonally to reflect modern social-emotional and STEM standards.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features" id="product">
        <!-- Feature 1: Physical Cards -->
        <div class="feature-block fade-in">
            <div class="feature-image card-mockup">
                <div class="floating-card">
                    <div class="bar" style="width: 40%"></div>
                    <div style="text-align: center; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 100px; font-size: 1.2rem;">APPLE</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
                <span class="section-tag">The Physical Tool</span>
                <h2>Tactile Illustration Cards</h2>
                <p>Our 36-card starter set features premium, spill-proof matte finishes with hand-drawn illustrations. Each card is sized perfectly for little hands to hold, flip, and discover.</p>
                <ul style="margin-top: 20px; list-style: none;">
                    <li>&#10048; Round edges for safety, hand-sized cards for easy transportation</li>
                    <li>&#10048; Simple, modern and vivid hand-drawn illustrations</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2: Digital Hub -->
        <div class="feature-block reverse fade-in">
            <div class="feature-image hub-mockup">
                <div class="screen-mini">
                    <div class="bar" style="background: var(--secondary); width: 30%"></div>
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; margin: 20px 0;">
                        <div style="flex: 1; height: 60px; background: #f0f0f0; border-radius: 8px;"></div>
                        <div style="flex: 1; height: 60px; background: #f0f0f0; border-radius: 8px;"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bar"></div>
                    <div class="bar"></div>
                    <div class="bar short"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
                <span class="section-tag">The Digital Brain</span>
                <h2>Modern Teacher Resource Hub</h2>
                <p>A sleek, mobile-ready dashboard for teachers. Track which cards are most popular in your class, download printable lesson plans, and access a library of pronunciation guides and songs.</p>
                <ul style="margin-top: 20px; list-style: none;">
                    <li>&#10048; Weekly lesson plan generator</li>
                    <li>&#10048; Student progress tracking</li>
                    <li>&#10048; Community forum for educators</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <h2>Ready to transform your classroom?</h2>
        <p style="margin: 20px 0; color: #b2bec3;">KidFit is currently in beta with 50 partner kindergartens.</p>
        <a href="#" class="cta-button">Contact the Team</a>
        <div style="margin-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #444; padding-top: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem;">
            &copy; 2026 KidFit Education. Made with ❤️ for early learners.
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="~/js/home.js"></script>
</body>
</html>